            "title": "盤中速報 - 道瓊指數大漲1.01%，報51361.11點",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間12日11:00，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>上漲512.36點（或1.01%），暫報51361.11點。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：-1.38%</li><li>近 1 月：+2.3%</li><li>近 3 月：+7.24%</li><li>近 6 月：+4.4%</li><li>今年以來：+5.8%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>成分股以高盛集團(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:GS:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/GS\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">GS-US</a>)領漲。高盛集團(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:GS:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/GS\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">GS-US</a>)上漲3.27%；漢威聯合國際(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:HON:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/HON\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">HON-US</a>)上漲2.67%；威瑞森電信(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:VZ:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/VZ\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">VZ-US</a>)上漲2.38%；摩根大通銀行(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:JPM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/JPM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">JPM-US</a>)上漲2.23%；威士卡(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:V:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/V\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">V-US</a>)上漲1.96%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>部分成分股表現相對疲軟，亞馬遜(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AMZN:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AMZN\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AMZN-US</a>)下跌2.02%；蘋果(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AAPL:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AAPL\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AAPL-US</a>)下跌1.49%；賽富時(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CRM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CRM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CRM-US</a>)下跌1.36%；波音(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:BA:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/BA\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">BA-US</a>)下跌1.07%；微軟(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MSFT:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MSFT\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MSFT-US</a>)下跌0.85%。</p></section></main>",
